        "subject": "LU-3373 llite: Update inode after setxattr",
        "message": "LU-3373 llite: Update inode after setxattr\n\nSince we don't revalidate inode anymore when atomic_open\nbe invoked. So need explicitly update inode info after\nsetxattr for acl permission check.\n\nSigned-off-by: yang sheng <yang.sheng@intel.com>\nChange-Id: If701fbbd3d9668e29a9ef81f8a15066af3d4578d\n"
